{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21041.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":300901,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"胡桃爱香","textRight":"那么……@为什么爱香我","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":300901}],"textRight":"非得陪你做这样的事情不可啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"阿见莉爱","textLeft":"有什么不行吗！@这是我陪你巡逻的谢礼！！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":200}],"textRight":"那份人情@我已经通过蛋包饭还清了！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"胡桃西餐厅的主厨@真是心胸狭窄……！"},{"chara":[{"id":300901,"motion":400}],"textRight":"这算什么意思啊……"},{"chara":[{"id":300901,"motion":0}],"textRight":"说到底，买本书而已，@你自己去不就行了吗……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"我要你扮演我的贴身保镖……！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":0}],"textRight":"哦……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300901}],"textRight":"说起来，@你手上拿的墨镜到底是什么……"},{"chara":[{"id":301001,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"当然是用来乔装打扮的！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301001}],"textLeft":"赶在发售日之前@就去购买刊登着自己的杂志，"},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"textLeft":"如果让这种谣言传播开来的话"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"会羞愧得活不下去了……！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"你平常做的事"},{"chara":[{"id":300901}],"textRight":"比这还要令人羞耻的多，@所以不要紧的。"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_movie12","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"找到了！这个！就是这个！@「BiBi」9月号！","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":300901,"motion":1}],"textRight":"喔……@就刊载在这上面吗，学姐？"},{"chara":[{"id":301001,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"对！@「原石女生」的页数是……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"58页……@找到了！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001}],"textLeft":"唔。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"诶，以初次登场来说，这种@刊载方式已经算非常隆重了吧？"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":400}],"textRight":"我看看……@啊，是八千代"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story01","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"[chara:301001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]啊！？八千代！？@七海八千代！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"你看，在这里。"},{"chara":[{"id":300901}],"textRight":"「八千代穿出的30日@服装搭配」……好像是这样？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"什么……@这、这算什么……！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":200}],"textRight":"噢噢……@八页的大型跨页刊载！"},{"chara":[{"id":301001,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"八……八页！？"},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"textLeft":"偏偏要上@我的初登场期刊！"},{"chara":[{"id":301001,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"这、这是一种@巧妙的挑衅方式！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":300}],"textRight":"怎么可能……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":301001,"motion":200}],"textBg":"shout","textLeft":"[chara:301001:effect_emotion_angry_1][se:7218_anger][flashEffect:flashWhite1]果然不可原谅！！！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"客、客人……！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"textRight":"学姐……一时冲动撕烂的杂志@请你自掏腰包买下哦！"},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face"